title: Broncos’ Manning slowing down? Raiders aren’t seeing it
text:
Photo: Jack Dempsey, Associated Press Peyton Manning, now 39, has led the Broncos to a 4-0 record and is now 42-10 in the regular season since joining Denver. Peyton Manning, now 39, has led the Broncos to a 4-0 record and is...
We might want to hold off on the changing-of-the-guard stories. You know, Peyton Manning on his way down, Derek Carr showing growth in his second season.
